k, og er blitt k\u00e5ret til \u00c5rets nettsted. Steiro har v\u00e6rt en avgj\u00f8rende kraft gjennom en lang periode, sier Munch til bt.no ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "439d2b7c4356481b768060296b00d062c5f27e9c069ade2ec42d73708d3ba456"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T22:01:51.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Gard Steiro (39) blir ny nyhetsredakt\u00f8r i VG."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11202951.ece/5b0oct/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Gard%20Steiro206.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/862cb0ba47b0945516e2a525bc58a11eb0715524.jpg?5945a1ee"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["BTs sjefredakt\u00f8r til VG -adressa.no", "- Vanskelig valg", "- Avgj\u00f8rende kraft"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "862cb0ba47b0945516e2a525bc58a11eb0715524"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["avgj\u00f8rende kraft", "jobb", "sjefredakt\u00f8r", "journalistikk", "redaksjon"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["vestlandet", "bergens tidende", "bergens tidenes", "\u00e5rets", "adresseavisen", "schibsted norge", "steiros"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["didrik munch", "gard steiro", "torry pedersen", "tor olav m\u00f8rseth"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11202951.ece/5b0oct/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Gard%20Steiro206.jpg"}, {"field": "o